---
---

<section id="comfort" class="comfort section section-dark">
  <div class="container comfort__inner">
    <div class="comfort__text reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Inside the network</p>
      <h2>The Indoor Comfort Guarantee.</h2>
      <p class="comfort__body">
        Every Waystation and Basecamp commits to climate-controlled indoor comfort, with
        comfortable restrooms, generous seating, and reliable high-speed Wi-Fi. The lounge is part
        of the standard, not an upsell.
      </p>
      <p class="comfort__body">
        At Summits, the hospitality extends further still, into overnight stays in modular
        Lookouts.
      </p>
    </div>

    <figure class="comfort__media frame duotone reveal">
      <img src="/images/basecamp-interior.jpg" alt="Interior of a Rangeway driver's lounge with warm lighting and comfortable seating" loading="lazy" />
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .comfort__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 0.92fr);
    gap: clamp(32px, 5vw, 80px);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .comfort__text {
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .comfort h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  .comfort__body {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 235, 0.84);
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  .comfort__body + .comfort__body {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  .comfort__media {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    align-self: stretch;
    min-height: 340px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .comfort__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }

    .comfort__media {
      order: -1;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      min-height: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
